# OMI_link

Link extension should be added to a node with the OMI_collider extension. Implementation details of how the link behaves (navigate on click or navigate on collide) is up to the client.

Metadata for the link can be gathered through a WebFinger-like API where you pass the URL and receive metadata like thumbnail, title, and description.

```json
{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "name": "Link",
      "extensions": {
        "OMI_link": {
          "uri": "https://omigroup.org/worlds/meetup"
        },
        "OMI_collider": {
          ...
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

